Introduction

TRENDZ is a seven-member boy group under Global H Media. They made their debut under Interpark Music Plus on January 5, 2022 with their first mini album Blue Set Chapter 1.


In July of 2021, Interpark announced that they had established a subsidiary label, Interpark Music Plus, for their idol group production business and revealed plans to debut a new boy group in January of 2022. Later that year it was revealed that Interpark Music Plus went out of business and the company's groups would work under Global H Media again.
